7th July 2015 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 4 Highlights

Stage 4 takes to the cobbles to pay tribute to Paris-Roubaix. With seven sections totalling just over 13km of pave, all the leaders and their teams will have to be super vigilant all day. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary from Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting reporting at the roadside.
